article_title: Bedbug problems stable, but the tiny bloodsuckers are still pests in Omaha

og.description: The number of calls about bedbugs has ticked up slightly in the past couple of weeks in the Omaha area, according to an insect expert. But he said he believes that the half-dozen additional calls over the past two weeks are largely a coincidence.
